Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That runt's not fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't working. Forget \Novertaking him, I can barely keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He always pulls \Naway on the corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! What\N the hell's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already riding on the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So why can't I catch up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one hell\N of a crash, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At least you're still in\N one piece, Beanpole.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then lemme give you some advice:\N your riding sucks.{ik this isn't grammatically correct btw - it's to be antagonising}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know riders can be clumsy, but if they end\N up wrecking their bike, then they ain't shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nothing like you\N young rich kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather break my\N neck than my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,With driving like that, the only time you'll overtake me is in your wildest dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes everything you've \Ngot just to not die in a crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That asshole...
