Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You've been lugging\N your 750 around town all day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to laugh \Nabout. I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd called me, \NI'd have brought the truck over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure didn't go \Neasy on it, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm sure there are a ton \Nof other mechanics on the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe you're right,\N but I managed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You managed? I don't think \Nany normal human would've.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You the Hulk or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How's she lookin'? {obvs bikes have she/her pronouns - so shut up}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine once \NI'm done with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a week and she'll\N be back up and running.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bike parts can be replaced easily enough, \Nbut I can't say the same for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, take care of yourself, \Nwill ya, Gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like you'll be making \Nit to class this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how's about \Nsome coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai! Hurry up or we're \Nleaving your butt behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignition.{if someone has a good onomatopoeia. lmk}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Vroom! Vroom, vrrroom!\N Vroom, vroom!{again, onomatopoeia, one of my many weaknesses}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you, Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating lunch out in the schoolyard has been more fun lately, or so it seems. {let's pretend that's what nanchatte means, kthx}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been dying to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai, what are you doing?\N C'mon, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I eat my lunch here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.\N I'm just trying to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, \NI won't bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been good \Nat this kind of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think \Nyou're going, bitch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,S-S-Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands off the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it got to \Ndo with you, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Doesn't matter what my deal is. \NAll that matters is I'm short-tempered.}Doesn't matter what. Worry about\N how I'm easy to piss off first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One of those delinquent types?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always had a thing for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Delinquents, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully I'm not \Nasking for too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you know someone \Nwho's good in a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,good at riding bikes,\N is really tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and has a gentle smile \Nwith perfect white teeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but he can't be ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And if this special someone drives a bike with \N400cc or more, you just have to introduce me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ito Ai, I'm in class 1-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid can you be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think there's \Nsomeone like that, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a 750cc, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much bigger \Nthan the Road Pal!{https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%9B%E3%83%B3%E3%83%80%E3%83%BB%E3%83%AD%E3%83%BC%E3%83%89%E3%83%91%E3%83%AB - I doubt anyone knows what a road pal is, maybe replace with a more friendly and familiar analogy, like "Girls' scooter"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to ride\N something like this, even just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, I saw one in a movie\N called High Teen Boogie. {https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%87%8E%E6%9D%91%E7%BE%A9%E7%94%B7 - likely this guy - might avoid for reasons idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The lead character in it\Nwas a bike gang leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so cool I could die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided I'd find my own gang leader,\N and fall in love with him, like in the movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My lunch got squashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm tryin' to sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't say another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:11:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you mind if my\N friends eat with u{\fscx200}—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ichikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.{avoiding ojou-san as cringe}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drop in like this.{note: under the impression that this is her place, and he went in to check the bikes without telling her}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be important\N for you to be here this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for the\N club's regular circuit, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get every machine \Nchecked over by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, we don't have a whole lotta participants this time round.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know anyone, \Nfeel free to bring 'em along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tsukuba Circuit,\N your favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind you riding \Naround at this time of night,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't go doing \Nanything stupid out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm begging you.}That's all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get myself in no fit state to get married, \NI'm all yours, Ichikawa.{kinda difficult to imply the nuance of "If I maim myself in a motorbike accident, I'm all yours"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I've already been married \Ntwice and have my own kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's getting late.\N I'll catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Side chick would suit me fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Like I could ever \Nafford two of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come and \Nget a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So whenever I couldn't find you, \Nyou'd be hiding around here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. Like I'd \Nbelieve that, you horndog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I can hardly believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She has some real nice legs...{https://jisho.org/search/%20%E3%81%82%E3%82%93%E3%82%88 ??? - not too sure of the word}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you see her flying around on \Na motorbike, hanging on for dear life... {it'll do, shh}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, Gun, \N your bike fixed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi asked if we wanted to go\N to Tsukuba Circuit on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! Anything but the bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it! He's had this \Ncomin' for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And breakin' his bike's the only \Nway we're gonna feel any better!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Damn it!\N- No, get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, he's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance!\N Go do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you so much as {\i1}touch{\i0} my CB, \NI'll make sure you regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You got away with \Na mild concussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not counting those scratches on \Nyour knees, elbows, and forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a strange one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you'd get \Nyourself hurt protecting my CB.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know why I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just didn't want them \Nto get their hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That bike was \Nshiny and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My bike would've been a \Nlot worse for wear without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to ride a bike, or something like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's only for a while, \NI can give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You really mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry, huh? \NI'll get you something in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"My dear Gun..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's been almost two years \Nsince you moved to Japan."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"It'd be nice if you could come see us in California over your summer vacation."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"My memory isn't what it used to be, and it'd be a shame to forget my only son's face, after all."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"I wish you could be here to see the blue \Nskies and blue seas of Santa Monica.{shh, it'll do}"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:18:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sending my love from L.A. \Nand across the Pacific - Dad."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That brings me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always been \Nquite the poet. {but he didn't know it, gotem}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Those in search of speed only ever arrive at one place, and that place is the circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been searching for it my whole \Nlife, and it's led me to one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:58.58,Default,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fs25}"Auto racing auxiliary facilities"{オートレース補助施設}{Yeah, too blurry to TS properly}{no longer too blurry to TS, but just happen to be too lazt to typeset}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we could've rode \Ntogether a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the circuit, huh? It's so \Nmuch bigger than I thought it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Best feeling ever. My spine's already tingling just from being here.{note}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure took your sweet time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a good reason for this.{/I had to do this}{actually, he says chotto meaning "I was a little forced to do this"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a long story, \Nso I'm not gonna go into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just how it is, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.\N Now who's the horndog?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice of you to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in need of a good race.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I okay to ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm about to race, \Nbut don't go wandering off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him. He's the one \Nthe Princess brought along.{note}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who that rich kid is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but how about we... \N'show him the ropes?' {idk how to make this sound ominous so shh}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Gun! It's your first time here,\N so go easy on the throttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get a feel for the course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong\N with those guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they were waiting \Nfor him to take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are some of \Nthe best drivers in our club,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but their manners \Nneed a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those jerks up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Those jerks...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure he was \Ngonna go flying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Blocking a newcomer from the inside line... talk about cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.62,0:23:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've gotta give him credit,\N it barely even fazed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.37,0:23:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This might get interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This greenhorn is trying \Nto make a move on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drive hard and \Nopen up the gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.72,0:24:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lookin' good! Damn good! \NGun blew past two of them on one lap!{should be "on" one lap imo }
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he great?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.57,0:24:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew he could\N ride a bike like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.15,0:24:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why people want\N to drive as fast as lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.24,0:24:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,On an unrelated note...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.62,0:24:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this girl to Gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.79,0:24:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is she? Pretty sure \NI'd like to know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.59,0:24:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Our eyes met.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.35,0:24:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens, \Nyou're supposed to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.37,0:25:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.49,0:25:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My bike's at its limit, \Nbut I can't pull away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.80,0:25:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Ichikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.63,0:25:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even have the basics down, \Nbut he's damn fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.26,0:25:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't exactly \Nseem like a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.01,0:25:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he's walking a tightrope \Non a windy day without a harness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.56,0:25:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna take a chance on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.69,0:25:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.86,0:25:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As he is now, he's more \Nlike a highway racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.78,0:25:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is insane! It took me ages to\Neven get anywhere near that lap time!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.04,0:26:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, this little punk...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.80,0:26:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm faster... I can take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.97,0:26:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all! It wasn't \Nsupposed to go like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.85,0:26:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No way am I gonna \Nlose to some greenho—
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.11,0:26:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass. You're going in too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.74,0:26:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Godammit! I ended up screwing \Nup my own throttle work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.42,0:26:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna go faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.31,0:27:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, I've seen more riders than I've been able to count.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.44,0:27:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've never seen \Nanyone ride like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.52,0:27:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.36,0:27:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You drive too fast to be \Nrelying on instinct alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.61,0:27:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Driving like that'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.03,0:27:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep racing at this level, I'm not \Nworried about you causing yourself harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.91,0:27:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're wanting to go faster, \NI'd quit while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.42,0:27:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you don't, that bike's\N gonna be the death of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.34,0:27:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.93,0:27:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a clue \Nwhat you're talking about.{me when Perevodildo says anything}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.26,0:27:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just ride because I wanna \Nbe faster than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.89,0:27:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.06,0:27:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll have to \Nchange the way you ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.65,0:27:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Instincts alone won't \Nget you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.90,0:27:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.07,0:27:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Think when you're riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.00,0:28:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.17,0:28:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he wanna talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.63,0:28:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what do you \Nthink about when you're driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.93,0:28:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.89,0:28:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.14,0:28:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What brought that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.81,0:28:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.94,0:28:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's get you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.56,0:28:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.44,0:28:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, speed racer!{meme ish line}{https://detail.chiebukuro.yahoo.co.jp/qa/question_detail/q12224998472}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.57,0:28:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're comin' next time, right?\N It'll be Suzuka or Fuji next time! {The FISCO circuit it the old name for the Fuji Speedway btw}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.29,0:28:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is just me thinkin', but I don't \Nthink you've got those hairpins down yet!{Tsukuba has 3 hairpins - one of which is fast, Fuji has between 1 and 3 depending on the layout - with the first one being like a 180-200mph top speed into a sharp hairpin - hence the sass}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.83,0:28:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go dyin' on us, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.25,0:28:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.13,0:28:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.30,0:28:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what people\N call bike buddies?{It's the best I can come up w/ atm}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.63,0:29:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome too, little lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.27,0:29:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.85,0:29:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.31,0:29:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it,\N I threw up a peace sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.48,0:29:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I'm with Gun,\N I get to see tons of new stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.07,0:29:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a brave new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.37,0:29:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently studying like\N mad to get my scooter license.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.25,0:29:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I pass my exams, I'll give Gun and Hiro a run for their money!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.21,0:29:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we have a new\N student starting in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.18,0:29:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hijiri. \NPlease, introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.60,0:29:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Osaka. \NHijiri Hideyoshi's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.64,0:29:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all about guts\N and nothin' else!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.06,0:29:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad habits are...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.65,0:29:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I get into fights all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.73,0:30:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,While I don't always start 'em,\N I always make sure to finish 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.86,0:30:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that dipshit \Nfrom the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.28,0:30:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you calling a\N dipshit, you little runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.08,0:30:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't gimme that shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.70,0:30:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.66,0:30:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't it obvious?! \NI transferred to this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.84,0:30:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Teach, I'm done! No way am I \Nstaying in the same class as this dipshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.21,0:30:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.80,0:30:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal? I'll see \Nthe principal myself if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.18,0:30:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so full of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.05,0:30:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, get yourself \Nexpelled for all I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.89,0:30:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?! You tryin' \Nto pick a fight with me, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.39,0:30:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's pickin' a fight \Nwith who, dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.40,0:30:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the stupidest \Nguy I've ever met!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.44,0:30:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a gorilla wouldn't\N pick a fight with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.65,0:30:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No shit! How'd one of them turn \Nup to school, you caveman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.24,0:30:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a caveman? \NYou little monkey man!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.28,0:30:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd ya say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.66,0:30:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.16,0:30:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What a buzzkill. Can't believe\N he's in the same class as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.92,0:31:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure was heating up in there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.84,0:31:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were gonna\N start swinging for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.47,0:31:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I can't stand that little runt \Nis because I lost to him on a bike before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.14,0:31:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's really that fast, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.52,0:31:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.94,0:31:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're not settling this with our fists,\N we're settling it on our bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.32,0:31:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.07,0:31:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't it obvious?\N I'm racing that little runt again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.37,0:31:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.37,0:31:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I need help!\N Miyuki has... Miyuki has—
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.62,0:31:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened to Mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.21,0:31:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Some strange guys showed up and\N forced Miyuki in the car with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.60,0:31:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru, what's the\N meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.40,0:32:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about that beanpole\N from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.65,0:32:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And we just need you out\N of the picture for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.16,0:32:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skull must be \Nthicker than your helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.16,0:32:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.83,0:32:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you're \Nso bent out of shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.29,0:32:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but it takes real scum to\N try something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.26,0:32:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bottom of the barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.80,0:32:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumors were right. You really are just some rich kid without a care in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.14,0:32:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you quite \Nrealize the situation you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.11,0:32:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you, m'lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.82,0:32:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.49,0:32:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure they\N said the riverbank?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.87,0:32:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.45,0:32:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro, get movin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.41,0:32:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have to ask me twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.80,0:33:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you looking \Nat me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.56,0:33:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You always have that look. You think you can see right into my head, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.69,0:33:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When I... joined the Ichinose Racing Team,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.69,0:33:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you were still in middle-school,\N but I couldn't help being drawn to you.{lol nonce}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.24,0:33:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands so delicate, \Nyet so steady with the machine,{華奢な手足でマシンをあやつり - with limbs that fragile/slender, controlling the machine}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.49,0:33:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and your form{physical appearance} through the corners...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.99,0:33:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd always been watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.54,0:33:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.83,0:33:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,since you've got money, you think\N you can look down on other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.17,0:33:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.29,0:33:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.63,0:33:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, money, status...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.42,0:33:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't you the one\N who's hung up on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.68,0:33:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.40,0:34:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't planned \Non doing this today,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.86,0:34:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but... but now I wanna\N teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.95,0:34:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Ichinose Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.20,0:34:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone so much as touches you, I'll make them regret being born!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.87,0:34:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.63,0:35:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the holdup, Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.30,0:35:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.17,0:35:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it! I'll do it\N on my own terms!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.56,0:35:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.72,0:35:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't cry and you don't beg.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.10,0:35:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Still too scared to show \Nyour own weakness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.48,0:35:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.56,0:35:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not lookin' so cute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.90,0:35:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just some woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.70,0:35:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, a girl should try to be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.95,0:35:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, you'll meet someone, \Nfall in love, and start your own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.46,0:35:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Those things are very\N important for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.67,0:35:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't interest \Nme in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.43,0:36:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what the big deal is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.64,0:36:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's how you think now,\N that's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.10,0:36:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Miyuki finds someone she likes more\N than her motorbike, she'll come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.46,0:36:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.42,0:36:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could've been a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.72,0:36:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, I'm sorry things\N turned out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.19,0:36:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.23,0:36:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A motorbike!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.53,0:36:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A CB750F!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.53,0:36:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.54,0:37:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that \Npunk would show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.21,0:37:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get our own back\N for the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.05,0:37:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you, punk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.76,0:37:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.30,0:37:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.68,0:37:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you do to the girl?! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.94,0:37:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.15,0:37:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass, we didn't do shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.70,0:37:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.45,0:37:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta the way!\N Move it, assholes!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.92,0:37:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.21,0:37:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you... how could \Nyou do that to Mi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.96,0:37:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.14,0:38:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.85,0:38:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.35,0:38:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back in ten years, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.23,0:38:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... I'd rather die than \Nlet you get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.48,0:38:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You kids can say just\N about anything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.61,0:38:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... that guy a \Nmonster or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.08,0:38:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a dead man!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.16,0:38:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See you in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.96,0:38:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.68,0:38:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.12,0:39:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.79,0:39:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... I thought he\N was just some rich kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.13,0:39:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How wrong could I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.11,0:39:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.57,0:39:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually kinda relieved\N when I heard your bike...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.28,0:39:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Any longer, and I might've done \Nsomething I could never take back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.29,0:39:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,On your feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.30,0:40:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen up, I'll never show myself in front of her as long as I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.64,0:40:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not giving up on riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.48,0:40:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If we happen to meet on the circuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.19,0:40:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,how about we settle things for good?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.94,0:40:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but you won't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.33,0:40:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.08,0:40:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not hurt, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.50,0:40:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.21,0:40:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.93,0:40:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst is already\N behind us, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.64,0:40:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.14,0:41:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As a boy, do you\N think I'm ugly?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.44,0:41:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.11,0:41:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're real cute,\N and smart too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.70,0:41:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.62,0:41:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I... like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.26,0:41:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.93,0:41:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, Mi suddenly collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.35,0:41:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we took her \Nstraight to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.60,0:41:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor told us she's got a bit of \Nanemia from the psychological shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.90,0:41:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.07,0:41:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.32,0:41:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't anything else\N we could do, so we went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.58,0:41:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.83,0:42:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I got something to eat,\N took a dump and went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.54,0:42:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.92,0:42:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.96,0:42:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why do you want\N to know every little detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.05,0:42:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.43,0:42:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was kinda worried about stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.56,0:42:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.60,0:42:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like her to be a downer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.44,0:42:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bra strap is about to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.77,0:42:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.61,0:42:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.33,0:42:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, dipshit?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.71,0:42:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You trying to pick a fight again?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.34,0:42:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning, 4:30. I'll be waiting for you at the same mountain pass as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.35,0:42:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.97,0:42:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,'Bout time I dealt with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.09,0:43:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, that runt...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.55,0:43:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's way better in\N the slower corners...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.89,0:43:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already starting\N to break away.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.68,0:43:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, at the next hairpin,\N I'm staying on him, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.82,0:43:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot. \NThis is no different from last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.82,0:44:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's got a\N screw loose for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.74,0:44:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He jumped his bike to\N get it back under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.92,0:44:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nipping at my heels.\NWhat's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.13,0:44:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How's he still on my tail\N with a driving style like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.14,0:44:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's chasing us?{/pursuing/following}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.18,0:44:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!\N What's that machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.57,0:44:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenging us both, huh? \NI'm ready when you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.83,0:44:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna occupy the inner line from the get-go? \NLike hell I'm letting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.26,0:44:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They overtook me!\N Who the hell is that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.22,0:45:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... that was smooth. \NI didn't even get to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.43,0:45:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You fired up, Beanpole?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.35,0:45:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna go, then go. \NNow's your chance, dipshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.60,0:45:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me\N if you crash out!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.02,0:45:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You really thought I'd back down?! I'm not goin' down without a fight! {shh, it'll do}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.71,0:45:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass, you think you \Ncan corner at that speed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.38,0:45:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You gotta be kiddin' me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.35,0:45:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's gonna hurt in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.65,0:45:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't hold back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.57,0:45:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't think anybody was \Nstupid enough to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.61,0:46:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither did I, but it\N kinda killed the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.55,0:46:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.26,0:46:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a chick...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.92,0:46:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.84,0:46:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, so you didn't \Nknow it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.43,0:46:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure \Nyou're okay to ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.85,0:46:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't show at school \Nyesterday, so I was worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.64,0:46:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I skipped yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.19,0:46:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one hell of a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.98,0:46:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.99,0:46:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't even know Formula 1 models. \NI'd be ashamed to be that stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.62,0:46:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.66,0:46:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always gotta \Nsay something, dontcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.25,0:46:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much of you to look at, but you're still an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.62,0:46:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, dipshit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.17,0:46:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Got something to say, ankle-biter?{何言ってやんでこのカメ男 - you heard me right, turtle man - no clue what's kame otoko, this seems to be this manga's original invention, it's not used as a common noun, maybe kame/turtle here means "little/short/something earthbound/not tall"}{yeah... I ain't got shit... so... shh}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.75,0:46:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt, \Nbut I've got places to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.50,0:47:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountains will have eroded by the time you're done arguing.{page 165 - ぐずぐずしてるとネズミが出るでしょう この辺 - she refers to the Aesop's fable of mountain giving birth to a mouse, but in manga this makes perfect sense as she adds "on this mountain" and before, the guys brag about with who got bigger balls for two pages straight, here however they merely throw names at each other and don't make big promises so even the meaning of the fable which is "a lot of big talk/malarkey with little results/ultimately fruitless" is inapplicable here, besides, barely anyone would get the reference; konohen is most likely "here/in this place" but I can't exclude "at this rate"}{Also, I hate this line : )}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.32,0:47:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I listened to Hiro \Nand came all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.57,0:47:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought people with skills \Nlike that would end up at my school.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.08,0:47:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposing...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.62,0:47:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposing I get those two together, \Nthey'd make the ultimate combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.83,0:47:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Next summer, things are gonna get \Ninteresting at Suzuka, and that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.12,0:48:16.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}I'll keep a smile on my face, \Neven when we say our goodbyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.96,0:48:20.38,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}Nervous yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.80,0:48:32.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}From the moment I wake up,\N I wanna ride{目覚めてく走りぬけてゆく} on the special street.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.81,0:48:44.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}{見せかけでもいい心のままに沈んでいたって}You can pretend all you want, but you can't hold on if your heart's not in the right place!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.28,0:48:50.99,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}{つかめない}I'm never letting go of my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.74,0:48:58.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}As we ride away, my tears \Nare swept away in the wind.{涙はスピードを揺らすから}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.92,0:49:02.67,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}Don't cry more. It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.25,0:49:11.55,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}Don't let the bustling \Nstreet corner get you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.55,0:49:15.35,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}Wink and kiss. It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.06,0:49:20.02,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}You're not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.62,0:49:37.75,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}I'm sure everyone's made \Nmistakes at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.75,0:49:44.54,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}So even if I lose my way,\N I'll keep on living!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.54,0:49:47.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fade(120,120)}Never stop!
